  <answer><![CDATA[<div class="c-page-content">
<p>Chalets are a popular option in France, offering full chalet service. In <a data-udi="umb://document/204ce8e4cf8c4ab09205501e16cb7565" href="/{localLink:umb://document/204ce8e4cf8c4ab09205501e16cb7565}" title="Tignes">Tignes</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/6d862a7043db4af4bd3aeba9ab6273fc" href="/{localLink:umb://document/6d862a7043db4af4bd3aeba9ab6273fc}" title="Chalet Les Arolles">Chalet Les Arolles</a> is in an ideal location close to resort and the beginners ski area. In <a data-udi="umb://document/16c56b283bca4ae2b2ada820a5d3a03d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/16c56b283bca4ae2b2ada820a5d3a03d}" title="Val d'Isere">Val d’Isere</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/b741a67aaee94a26bd6d0e0112846efc" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b741a67aaee94a26bd6d0e0112846efc}" title="Hotel &amp; Spa Le Savoie">Hotel &amp; Spa Le Savoie</a> is based in the resort centre and a favourite with guests.</p>
